I faced while playing a Human Priestess of Bertoxxulous.<br>
<br>
--I was KOS-threatening to all Barbarians.  (groan)<br>
--I could do nothing to increase Halas faction.  (scream)<br>
<br>
--Gnolls still killed me even though I worshipped the<br>
  Plaguebringer, which those in BB do also. (groan)<br>
--I could do nothing to increase this faction. (scream)<br>
<br>
--I had no nightvision as a Human. (groan)<br>
--I could barely see to zone into my guild. (scream)<br>
<br>
--My base WIS as a Human Priestess was 110. (groan)<br>
--I ran out of mana super-fast, even at level 9. (scream)<br>
<br>
--I am KOS to wolves and bears at all levels. (groan)<br>
--I can't even do Ranger/Druid-type quests to increase<br>
  faction with the QRG Protected Animals. (scream)<br>
<br>
--I am KOS to all Dwarves, Erudite Heretics in Paineel,<br>
  High Elves, Wood Elves, Ogres, Trolls, and Iksar. <br>
  (groan), and maybe Dark Elves too. (groan)<br>
--I can do nothing to increase any of these factions <br>
  except the Paineel Heretics. (scream)<br>
<br>
--The Frogloks automatically/initially hate me. (groan)<br>
--My faction with them can only get worse. (scream)<br>
<br>
Bottom line:  If you worship the Plaguebringer, almost<br>
EVERYONE hates you and wants to kill you on sight, and that's just the strictest roleplayers! :-) LOL!  <br>
<br>
How the heck did Ulec get to 60?<br>
Even the Teir'Dal have Ultravision, 118 base WIS, and<br>
semi-allies in Oggok and Grobb, 2 tough evil cities.<br>
<br>
I'm going with a Veeshan Bard or a Karana Ranger.<br>
I'm 90% there.  Sorry, Bertoxxulous, but I've tried you<br>
three times before (Terris-Thule twice as Lacquesis, <br>
FV as Atrilinea), and I tried REALLY REALLY HARD,<br>
but I never made it past 12.  Exp loss sucks!!!  <br>
<br>
Your desperate comrade,<br>
Waxalijen (that Dwarf NPC hit me so hard I can't even<br>
think in order to spell my name right!) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/utzarothfv.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tzaroth FV</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 49<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(8/9/02 10:49:16 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm45.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=58.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Bertoxxulous Cleric Hazards</span><hr size=1> What about Gnomes? Are they KOS? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/urhaxalygen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rhaxalygen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 156<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(8/9/02 11:02:38 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm45.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=58.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> If Gnomes worship the Plaguebringer and are Clerics...</span><hr size=1> Gnome Clerics of Bertoxxulous...<br>
