There are undead all the way to 60 if you look.  But the cleric's path in general is tough.  If you think that is tough, try being a rogue.  I got my rogue to 60 but I can't do a group class again or I would be a Bertox cleric of ak anon or maybe a warrior.  No real solo ability post 30 and difficult post 20.  Any group class like the warrior, enchanter, cleric or rogue have it tough and need support but tend to be essential.<br>
<br>
